{"error": null, "result": {"nr": 383, "upvote_ids": [], "change_log": [{"type": "create", "when": "2015-05-04T01:36:25Z", "uid": "i74g3aomM8b", "data": "i997ut7vq804pr", "anon": "no"}, {"uid": "hdjoucuyb836fq", "to": "i997ut7pkf14pq", "when": "2015-05-04T01:52:16Z", "anon": "no", "data": "i998f77vjl96iy", "type": "i_answer"}, {"type": "followup", "to": "i997ut7pkf14pq", "when": "2015-05-04T03:26:36Z", "uid": "i74g3aomM8b", "anon": "no"}, {"type": "feedback", "to": "i997ut7pkf14pq", "when": "2015-05-04T07:17:39Z", "uid": "hdjoucuyb836fq", "anon": "no"}, {"type": "feedback", "to": "i997ut7pkf14pq", "when": "2015-05-04T12:00:42Z", "uid": "i74g3aomM8b", "anon": "no"}, {"type": "feedback", "to": "i997ut7pkf14pq", "when": "2015-05-05T11:50:27Z", "uid": "hxu22d7okof4c1", "anon": "no"}], "q_edits": [], "i_edits": [], "unique_views": 43, "bookmarked": 4, "config": {}, "history": [{"subject": "pa2page(*ptep)这样写对吗&#xff1f;", "content": "<p>在pmm.c里面有多处pa2page(*ptep)这样的写法&#xff0c;应该写成pte2page(*ptep)才对吧&#xff1f;虽然结果一样&#xff0c;但是意义是不一样的吧&#xff1f;</p>", "created": "2015-05-04T01:36:25Z", "uid": "i74g3aomM8b", "anon": "no"}], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "request_instructor_me": false, "folders": ["lab2"], "type": "question", "tag_good": [{"class_sections": ["课程设计_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "清华学生_i5j09fnsl7k5x0"], "admin": true, "role": "instructor", "facebook_id": null, "us": false, "name": "Yu Chen", "id": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "photo": "1378950179_35.png"}], "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-05-04T01:36:25Z", "t": 1433500460180, "id": "i997ut7pkf14pq", "status": "active", "tag_good_arr": ["hcrrjuyequh4bt"], "default_anonymity": "no", "my_favorite": false, "bucket_order": 2, "is_bookmarked": false, "is_tag_good": false, "bucket_name": "Today", "no_answer_followup": 0, "children": [{"folders": [], "bucket_order": 2, "config": {}, "history": [{"subject": "", "content": "<p>pa2page也可以&#xff0c;因为*ptep的高22位确实是物理地址&#xff0c;而pa2page就是找到物理地址对应的page结构的&#xff08;pa2page不care传进来的物理地址的低12位&#xff09;。只是使用pa2page之前必须确认*ptep是有效的pte。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>pte2page只是pa2page的一个封装而已&#xff0c;用哪一个意义上都是一样的。</p>", "created": "2015-05-04T01:52:16Z", "uid": "hdjoucuyb836fq", "anon": "no"}], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "bucket_name": "Today", "is_tag_endorse": false, "children": [], "tag_endorse": [], "tag_endorse_arr": [], "created": "2015-05-04T01:52:16Z", "id": "i998f77qk6h6ix", "type": "i_answer"}, {"no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "i74g3aomM8b", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "bucket_order": 3, "updated": "2015-05-04T03:26:36Z", "config": {}, "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "data": {"embed_links": null}, "anon": "no", "folders": [], "subject": "<p>这仅仅是一个巧合吧&#xff0c;因为pte中代表地址的是前22位&#xff0c;而现在的内存管理是一个Page结构对应4096位&#xff0c;恰好是把高22位相同的用一个Page结构管理而已。</p>\n<p>如果这两个不都是4096位&#xff0c;或是我可以把低22位相同的用Page结构管理&#xff0c;或是有可能在64位或是其他体系结构的CPU中pte定义不同&#xff0c;这些情况下pa2page和pte2page是不一样的吧&#xff1f;</p>\n<p>现在我想问的是一种严谨、通用的写法&#xff0c;不能仅仅因为现在能工作、或是仅仅在目前情况下&#xff0c;通不通过PTE_ADDR对PPN的结果没影响就说它们的意义是一样的吧&#xff1f;如果意义一样的话当时也不会特地定义这两个函数对吧&#xff1f;</p>", "children": [{"d-bucket": "Yesterday", "uid": "hdjoucuyb836fq", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "bucket_order": 3, "updated": "2015-05-04T07:17:39Z", "config": {}, "anon": "no", "data": {"embed_links": null}, "folders": [], "subject": "<p>你的想法很好&#xff0c;这正是在让一个内核同时支持多种体系架构特别需要注意的地方。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>1、page用22位和pte用22位不是巧合&#xff0c;因为page结构在设计时就是用来管理物理页的&#xff0c;要是不遵从硬件对物理页的划分方法&#xff0c;那就变成其他数据结构&#xff0c;而不是我们期望的page了&#xff1b;</p>\n<p>2、能让pte2page和pa2page不同的情况&#xff0c;可能包括页表项中的页帧号不存放在最高部分&#xff0c;或者页表项中存放的不是页帧号&#xff0c;而是其它什么东西。如果要兼顾所有这些可能的情况&#xff0c;那确实需要考虑在体系架构无关的代码中用pte2page替换pa2page&#xff0c;在ucore lab里涉及get_page中用到pa2page的一处。</p>\n<p>3、最早实现了一个pte2page应该只是用作pa2page处理pte的shortcut&#xff0c;ucore lab设计之初并没有考虑支持多架构的需求。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>谢谢指出&#xff01;</p>", "children": [], "type": "feedback", "created": "2015-05-04T07:17:39Z", "id": "i99k1nd97q9el"}, {"d-bucket": "Yesterday", "uid": "i74g3aomM8b", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "bucket_order": 3, "updated": "2015-05-04T12:00:42Z", "config": {}, "anon": "no", "data": {"embed_links": null}, "folders": [], "subject": "<p>也就是我的理解没错喽&#xff1f;</p>", "children": [], "type": "feedback", "created": "2015-05-04T12:00:42Z", "id": "i99u5nsmip34df"}, {"uid": "hxu22d7okof4c1", "bucket_name": "Today", "bucket_order": 2, "updated": "2015-05-05T11:50:27Z", "config": {}, "anon": "no", "data": {"embed_links": null}, "folders": [], "subject": "<p>从业务逻辑的角度看&#xff0c;我会尽量用pte2page。</p>", "children": [], "type": "feedback", "created": "2015-05-05T11:50:27Z", "id": "i9b98bnqixr75k"}], "type": "followup", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-05-04T03:26:36Z", "id": "i99bsirdzrl71b"}], "request_instructor": 0, "tags": ["lab2", "student"], "s_edits": [], "num_favorites": 0}, "aid": "iajh5u38z3d4x1"}